Transaction went well.  Items were described as "like new" and came in sealed plastic, but the actual movie discs for all 3 movies were loose in their respective cases when they arrived.  Needless to say, they are quite scratched-up, and will most likely be skipping in a matter of time.  Unfortunately these were a gift, and I gambled on them working properly instead of returning them.  I really hope they work well for the gift recipient.
